{"tid":1449772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以幫手搞份文宣，叫中國人顧掂自己先好多管香港既閒事","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:47:29.000Z","uid":172349,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7509c9af2214ecda9d5616f42b070daf8d2fbc97","tid":1449772,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"想要中國人先顧掂自己基本生活，先好多管香港既閒事<br />\n<br />\n包括:<br />\n放心飲水喉開出黎既水<br />\n確認自己呼吸既係乾淨空氣<br />\n係屋企附近就買到安全奶粉<br />\n唔洗擔心自己細路係學校食發莓午餐<br />\n一人有病，全家富變貧<br />\n<br />\n請佢地顧掂自己基本生活保障先好多管香港既閒事<br />\n<br />\n同埋解釋同係中國既地方，點解香港有佢地無<br />\n<br />\n而且要鼓勵佢地爭取更好既生活<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99446c120805c683eb5cfb4e9103f78302a00fc","tid":1449772,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfbeefb6a50011f3da4c723ab56c26f71ff82ab","tid":1449772,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5252f57ab834162596e7c460cb2952c05f83837a","tid":1449772,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:47:07.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"8673f59f158327e030eb96e240c81316db24152e","tid":1449772,"uid":61343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:48:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4e9286b417f82459ffb3cb3dd7b108826ef98db","tid":1449772,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:14:52.000Z","msg":"重有佢地有盲點兩個<br />\n<br />\n1: 社會有亂，佢地都覺得係政府無錯，其實唔係人民錯就係政府錯，真係想問問佢地大躍進餓死三千萬人係咪因為中國人太懶，叫佢地一介蟻民唔好成日用統治階層既思想思考<br />\n2:佢地好多人唔知自己收既資訊唔全面，唔知佢地睇既新聞係經過挑選先比佢地睇，佢地唔知件事既另一面"},{"pid":"3a5cbbf53196c6784531172e6ad0c1d14ba18184","tid":1449772,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8390ae9782a8f4778bb4a3b6eede35a76029f1e","tid":1449772,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6866f8a1790300b83aca322871fa7a873410e9","tid":1449772,"uid":262737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:44:31.000Z","msg":"對福建幫意圖襲擊港人&lsquo;愛國義舉&rsquo;既神級回應<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1433143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1433143</a>"},{"pid":"102a10e6ec6c5de2c38819f2df093fff7addf7f4","tid":1449772,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1bf600f92c705df97643e73d18353bec34aa57","tid":1449772,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:44:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5edec36346c96ceb6293fbfa9ce0ec370fc4d292","tid":1449772,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:49:44.000Z","msg":"[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a>"},{"pid":"ad92b53abc2dfba7d991b30d985ed2d4422bc36f","tid":1449772,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6342dd5471383d1dc5ed62c22bca8d807818f83","tid":1449772,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cl